{"_path":"/health/h010","_dir":"health","_draft":false,"_partial":false,"_locale":"","title":"脂肪肝","description":null,"image":null,"sequence":10,"category":"認識疾病","link":null,"head":{"meta":[{"name":"keywords","content":""},{"name":"robots","content":""},{"name":"author","content":""},{"name":"copyright","content":"© 2024 A7新林口 - 社區網站"},{"name":"og:title","content":"健康休閒"}]},"publishedAt":"2025-04-17T00:00:00.000Z","toc":true,"body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"脂肪肝"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"脂肪肝"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"什麼是脂肪肝"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"什麼是脂肪肝？"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"脂肪肝（Fatty Liver Disease）是指肝臟內脂肪堆積過多，特別是三酸甘油酯（triglycerides）含量超過肝臟正常範圍（通常大於 5-10%）。脂肪肝分為兩大類："}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ol","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"非酒精性脂肪肝病（NAFLD）"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：與代謝問題（如肥胖、糖尿病、胰島素阻抗）相關，不因飲酒引起。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"酒精性脂肪肝病（AFLD）"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：由長期過量飲酒導致。"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"脂肪肝可能無症狀，但若不處理，可能進展為脂肪性肝炎（NASH）、肝纖維化，甚至肝硬化或肝癌。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"hr","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"如何預防脂肪肝"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"如何預防脂肪肝？"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ol","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"控制體重"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：保持健康體重（BMI 18.5-24.9），避免肥胖。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"健康飲食"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：減少高糖、高脂食物攝取，增加蔬果、全穀類攝取。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"規律運動"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：每周至少 150 分鐘中等強度有氧運動（如快走、游泳）或 75 分鐘高強度運動，搭配肌力訓練。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"限制酒精"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：避免過量飲酒，男性每日不超過 20-30g 酒精（約 2 杯啤酒），女性不超過 10-20g。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"管理慢性疾病"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：控制糖尿病、高血壓、高血脂等代謝疾病。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"避免不必要藥物"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：避免濫用可能損害肝臟的藥物或補充劑。"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"hr","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"如何保養脂肪肝"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"如何保養脂肪肝？"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"若已診斷脂肪肝，保養重點在於減緩病情進展並促進肝臟健康："}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ol","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"減重"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：若超重，逐步減重（每周 0.5-1 公斤），目標減掉 5-10%體重，能顯著改善肝脂肪。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"定期檢查"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：每 6-12 個月追蹤肝功能（ALT、AST）、超音波或影像檢查，監控病情。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"避免肝臟負擔"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：減少飲酒、避免暴露於毒素（如農藥、化學物質）。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"戒菸"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：吸菸可能加重肝臟炎症，應戒除。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"充足睡眠"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：維持規律作息，避免熬夜，幫助代謝平衡。"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"hr","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"如何飲食"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"如何飲食？"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"脂肪肝飲食應以低脂、低糖、高纖為原則，參考地中海飲食模式："}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ol","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"增加健康脂肪"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：\n"},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"攝取富含 Omega-3 的食物，如深海魚（鮭魚、鯖魚）、亞麻籽、奇亞籽。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"使用橄欖油取代動物油或反式脂肪。"}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"多吃蔬果與高纖食物"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：\n"},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"每天至少 5 份新鮮蔬果，提供維生素、抗氧化劑。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"全穀類（如糙米、燕麥、藜麥）及豆類，幫助穩定血糖。"}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"減少精緻糖與高 GI 食物"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：\n"},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"避免含糖飲料、甜點、蛋糕、白麵包等，這些會促進脂肪堆積。"}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"控制飽和脂肪與紅肉"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：\n"},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"減少肥肉、加工肉品（如香腸、培根）、奶油攝取。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"選擇瘦肉、去皮雞肉或植物性蛋白（如豆腐）。"}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"適量蛋白質"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：\n"},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"攝取優質蛋白，如雞蛋、魚類、瘦肉、低脂乳製品，支持肝臟修復。"}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"限制鹽分"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：\n"},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"每日鈉攝取量低於 2300mg，避免水腫及高血壓。"}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"多喝水，少喝酒"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：\n"},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"每天飲水 1.5-2 公升，促進代謝。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"避免酒精，特別是酒精性脂肪肝患者需完全戒酒。"}]}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"具體飲食建議"}]},{"type":"text","value":"："}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"早餐"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：燕麥粥搭配藍莓、奇亞籽，配無糖豆漿。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"午餐"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：糙米飯、蒸魚、燙青菜、少許橄欖油調味。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"晚餐"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：雞胸肉沙拉（菠菜、番茄、鷹嘴豆），以檸檬汁調味。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"點心"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：堅果（無鹽杏仁、核桃）、新鮮水果。"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"hr","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"其他注意事項"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"其他注意事項"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"避免快速減重"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：過快減重可能加重肝臟負擔，應循序漸進。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"諮詢專業人士"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：與醫師或營養師討論個人化飲食與治療計畫。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"心理健康"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：壓力可能影響飲食與代謝，適時透過冥想、瑜伽減壓。"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"透過健康生活方式，脂肪肝大多可逆轉或控制，關鍵在於長期堅持！"}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[{"id":"脂肪肝","depth":3,"text":"脂肪肝"},{"id":"什麼是脂肪肝","depth":3,"text":"什麼是脂肪肝？"},{"id":"如何預防脂肪肝","depth":3,"text":"如何預防脂肪肝？"},{"id":"如何保養脂肪肝","depth":3,"text":"如何保養脂肪肝？"},{"id":"如何飲食","depth":3,"text":"如何飲食？"},{"id":"其他注意事項","depth":3,"text":"其他注意事項"}]}},"_type":"markdown","_id":"content:health:h010.md","_source":"content","_file":"health/h010.md","_extension":"md"}